'''Jeff Grubb''' is an author and game designer. He has worked on a number of computer and role-playing games and has written a number of successful novels, short stories and comics. His credits include [[Wikipedia:List of Forgotten Realms novels#The Finder's Stone Trilogy|''The Finder's Stone Trilogy'']] with his wife, [[Wikipedia:Kate Novak|Kate Novak]], the [[Wikipedia:Spelljammer|''Spelljammer'']] and the [[Wikipedia:Jakandor|''Jakandor'']] campaign settings, and, more recently, the computer games [[Wikipedia:Guild Wars Nightfall|''Guild Wars Nightfall'']].

